SUMMARY

UrbanPlus is a free YMAP modification for Grand Theft Auto V, FiveM, and RageMP.

You are allowed to use it, edit it, run it on servers, include it in modpacks,
share it, mirror it, and use it in monetized servers or communities.

The main restrictions are simple:

- Do not claim you created the original work.
- Do not remove SantosMods.dev credit from official files.
- Do not sell UrbanPlus by itself as your own product.
- Do not use UrbanPlus for illegal, malicious, or abusive purposes.

----------------------------------------------------------------

1. WORK COVERED BY THIS LICENSE

UrbanPlus: World Reimagined ("UrbanPlus" or "the Work") is a free YMAP
modification created and distributed by SantosMods.dev.

UrbanPlus may include:

- YMAP files
- Map edits
- Placement data
- Models
- Textures
- Scripts
- Configuration files
- Metadata
- Documentation
- Related project files

This license applies only to the original work created or distributed by
SantosMods.dev.

2. OFFICIAL DISTRIBUTION LOCATIONS

The official and authorized distribution locations for UrbanPlus are:

- https://santosmods.dev/ (Main Location)
- https://www.lcpdfr.com/
- https://thedevhub.org/

UrbanPlus may also be shared or mirrored elsewhere under this license, but
SantosMods.dev only guarantees authenticity, updates, and support for versions
published through the official locations listed above.

3. PERMITTED USE

You may use UrbanPlus freely.

You are allowed to:

- Use UrbanPlus in Grand Theft Auto V
- Use UrbanPlus on FiveM servers
- Use UrbanPlus on RageMP servers
- Use UrbanPlus on public servers
- Use UrbanPlus on private servers
- Use UrbanPlus in development servers
- Use UrbanPlus in roleplay communities
- Use UrbanPlus in non-roleplay communities
- Use UrbanPlus in personal projects
- Use UrbanPlus in community projects
- Use UrbanPlus in server packs
- Use UrbanPlus in modpacks
- Use UrbanPlus in mirrors or archives
- Use UrbanPlus in videos, screenshots, streams, trailers, or promotional media

You do not need written permission from SantosMods.dev for normal use.

4. MODIFICATION RIGHTS

You may modify UrbanPlus.

You are allowed to:

- Edit files
- Move objects
- Remove objects
- Add objects
- Rename files
- Change layouts
- Adjust compatibility
- Merge UrbanPlus into a larger server pack
- Convert or adapt files for compatible GTA V multiplayer use
- Make custom versions for your own server or project

Modified versions are allowed.

If you publish a modified version, you should make it clear that it is modified
and not an official SantosMods.dev release.

Suggested label:

"Modified version of UrbanPlus: World Reimagined. Original project by SantosMods.dev."

5. REDISTRIBUTION RIGHTS

You may redistribute UrbanPlus for free.

You are allowed to:

- Reupload the original files
- Reupload modified files
- Include UrbanPlus in a free modpack
- Include UrbanPlus in a server resource pack
- Share UrbanPlus with staff or developers
- Share UrbanPlus in Discord servers
- Share UrbanPlus through mirrors
- Archive UrbanPlus for preservation

You should include this license when redistributing UrbanPlus.

6. MONETIZED SERVER USE

UrbanPlus may be used on monetized servers and communities.

You are allowed to use UrbanPlus on servers that have:

- Donations
- Tebex stores
- Paid perks
- Paid whitelist access
- VIP systems
- Subscriptions
- Sponsorships
- Advertisements
- Paid hosting
- Commercial community operations

UrbanPlus may be part of a server, community, or gameplay experience that earns
money.

You do not need special permission for this.

7. COMMERCIAL LIMITATION

You may not sell UrbanPlus by itself as your own standalone product.

You may not:

- Claim UrbanPlus is your original creation
- Sell the original UrbanPlus files as your own product
- Sell a lightly edited version of UrbanPlus as your own product
- Remove SantosMods.dev credit from official files
- Misrepresent yourself as SantosMods.dev
- Misrepresent your version as an official SantosMods.dev release

This does not prevent monetized server use.

This does not prevent use in paid communities.

This does not prevent use in a larger server pack, community pack, or gameplay
environment.

